quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  10,89,"Nyasaye naboola mbu; “Okhusaba khwenyu khuchamilwe, kholaano yeme obulayi, ne mulalonda tsinjila tsia balia abalamanya tawe.”"
  10,90,"Nikhwambusia Abaana ba Israili Inyanza, ne Firauni nende omukanda kukwe kwa abalwani nabalondakhwo khububii nende khubusuku. Okhula shingala Firauni yanyoolwa nende lifwa liokhusishibwa mumatsi, naboola mbu; “Esuubile mbu abulaho Nyasaye wundi halali wa Abana ba Israili basuubila, nasi endi halala nende abandu belekhulila Nyasaye (Abasalamu).”"
  10,91,"Oooh! Bulano buri? Ne wali wakhaya, mana noba mubandu bokhuhononia."
  10,92,"Kho inyanga ino khwitsa okhuhabina omubili kukwo kho obe eshimanyisio khubetsa inyuma wuwo. Ne toto abandu abaanji bang’ang’ala ehale nende ebimanyasio biefu."
  10,93,"Ne toto Abana ba Israili khwabamenyia obulayi, ne nikhubahelesia emikabo emilayi. Ne shibakabukhana tawe okhula shinga obumanyi bwaboolela. Toto Nyasaye wabu Omulesi alikhalaka eshina hakari wabu inyanga yeyindukho khukalia akabakabukhanilangamwo."
  10,94,"Ne noli nende inganakani nende khuka khwakhwishilia, mana reeba abasomanga eshitabu ewe noshiili. Toto obulamba bumalile okhukhwitsila okhurula khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi. Kho olakhatema waba mubalia bali nende obukanakani tawe."
  10,95,"Ne olakhatema waba mubalia bakatsula ebimanyisio bia Nyasaye tawe, wakhetsa waba mubalia basikha."
  10,96,"Toto balia belikhuwa lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi liamala okhubaburira shibasuubilanga tawe."
  10,97,"Kata nibetselwa nende buli eshimanyisio (shibanyala okhusuubila tawe), okhula balole eshinyasio eshilulu."